chunk_content: For this indicator, a “PEPFAR-supported site” should include any facility site in the PEPFAR geographic organizational hierarchy list in DATIM, which also reported any site-level programmatic target or result during the same reporting period. Omit facilities which were previously supported by PEPFAR but were not assigned any targets nor reported any results for any program area during the same reporting period. Include all health care workers irrespective of whether any or all are receiving PEPFAR support. We do NOT need any workers reported at the community level for this indicator; workers supported by the government or other organizations, but not based out of a PEPFAR supported facility should not be reported. HIV/AIDS has placed significant demands on the already constrained health workforce in many low- income countries. The rapid scale-up of ART is placing additional demands on the health workforce.
